Description: A button in the expedition failed screen, that restarts (loads) the game at the latest checkpoint.

French.Translation: Redémarrer depuis le dernier point de contrôle

Spanish.Translation: Reiniciar desde el último punto de control

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Reiniciar no último ponto de controle

Japanese.Translation: 最後のチェックポイントから再開

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 從最近的重生點重新開始

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 从最近的重生点重新开始

name: ExpeditionFailPage.RestartCheckpointButton
